    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ Nos <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/167">Landolfus</persName>
                        divina ordinante providentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps"
                            >princeps</rs> per rogum <persName key="##Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"
                            ref="#people/2444">Gariperti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">castaldei</rs> dilecti nostri concedimus
                        in <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Abbots #Monasteries #Other_basins #Fish #Wildfowl #Game #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Rivers #Riverbed #Canals #Roads"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti Benedicti maiori</orgName>, ubi nunc
                        Dei fabente domnus <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/309"
                            >Aligernus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> et spiritualis pater noster praesse bidetur,
                            <rs key="#Other_basins #Rivers">aqua</rs> quae dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Other_basins #Fish #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/2846">Anclena</placeName>, incipiente de ipsu poritu quae
                        vocatur <placeName
                            key="#Other_basins #Rivers #Fish #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Lapillusu</placeName> et qualiter vadit et ungit se in alia aqua que
                        dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Other_basins #Rivers #Fish #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Aucla</placeName>, nec non et alii aqua quae nominatur fossatu de
                            <placeName
                                key="#Other_basins #Rivers #Canals #Fish #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Ortellu</placeName> qualiter exiit de ipsi <rs key="#Canals"
                            >canali</rs> et badit et iungit secum praedicta aqua de eadem Anclena,
                        simul et alias aqua quae dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Other_basins #Rivers #Fish ##Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >Bareca</placeName>, quae est inter praedictam aqua de eadem Anclena, et
                        iam dicto fossatu et iungit se haec aqua cum iam dicta aqua quae exitit de
                        praedicto fossatu. Haec autem iam phata aquis cum ripis suis ex utraque
                        parte positae et cum <rs key="#Riverbed">albeis</rs> et <rs key="#Roads"
                            >viis</rs> suis ibidem intrandi et exiendi, ibique in predicto
                        monasterio concessimus habendi ac possidendi, atque <rs
                            key="#Fish #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">piscandi</rs> vel
                            <rs key="#Wildfowl #Game"> aucellandi</rs>, et faciendi ibi omnia quae
                        pars iamphati monasterii et eius rectoribus placuerit et iusserit, absque
                        contrarietate cuiuscumque persona hominis, ut perpetuis temporibus predicto
                        monasterio habeant et possideant, neminem suis abbatibus et rectoribus in
                        aliquo contraria ingerente. Quod si quispiam hanc nostram concessionem in
                        quomodocumque violare presumpserit, sciat se in praefato sancto monasterio
                        et eius abbatibus atque rectoribus compositurus auri optimi libras quinque,
                        et haec concessio de quibus continet firma et stabilis maneat semper.
                        Scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Petrus"
                            >Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> ex iussione supradicta potestatis in anno
                        quartodecimo principatus eius, mense novembrio, indictione undecima. Actum
                        in <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capuana</placeName>.</ab>
